            "--- Membaca Metadata & Deteksi Kolom ---\n",
            "✅ Pemetaan Kolom Berhasil:\n",
            "   - Gambar  : 'Image Name'\n",
            "   - Pasien  : 'Patient'\n",
            "   - Label   : 'Label'\n",
            "   - Kualitas: 'Quality Score'\n",
            "\n",
            "✅ Data Terbagi! Train: 558, Val: 97, Test: 92\n",
            "\n",
            "--- Verifikasi Batch Gambar ---\n",
            "Shape Tensor Gambar: torch.Size([4, 3, 224, 224])\n",
            "Label GON+/GON-    : tensor([1, 1, 1, 1])\n",
            "Skor Kualitas (0-1): tensor([0.5700, 0.5460, 0.5970, 0.4150])\n",
